data.description: Experience the charm of this delightful corner lot property with an 8 ft gate located in the serene neighborhood of Rancho Bella Vista. Discover an inviting interior, featuring tile and carpet flooring, neutral palette, and a spacious living area. The heart of the home is the delightful kitchen, equipped with SS appliances, white shaker cabinets, granite counters, and a practical breakfast bar, making it a joy to prepare meals in. Spacious loft area offers an ideal space for an entertainment center. Main bedroom offers an ensuite with dual sinks and a walk-in closet. Outside, the serene backyard beckons with a covered patio and fruit trees,  offering ample space to design your dream pool or unleash your creative landscaping ideas. What's not to like? Come and make it yours today!
